---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: "Contact"
seoDescription: "Contactez la rédaction du Smash Club pour vos questions, partenariats ou suggestions sur le padel et le pickleball."
permalink: /contact/
---

<div class="container--narrow">
    <header class="page-header">
        <h1 class="page-header__title">Contact</h1>
        <p class="page-header__subtitle">Une question, une suggestion, une idée d'article ? Écrivez-nous.</p>
    </header>

    <div class="page-body">
        <form class="contact-form" name="contact" method="POST" data-netlify="true">
            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="name">Nom</label>
                <input type="text" id="name" name="name" placeholder="Votre nom" required>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="email">Email</label>
                <input type="email" id="email" name="email" placeholder="votre@email.com" required>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="subject">Sujet</label>
                <input type="text" id="subject" name="subject" placeholder="De quoi s'agit-il ?" required>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="message">Message</label>
                <textarea id="message" name="message" placeholder="Votre message..." required></textarea>
            </div>
            <button type="submit" class="form-submit">Envoyer →</button>
        </form>
    </div>
</div>
